      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 14</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>As long as you are moving at Speed Rank 1 or higher, you gain the benefits of the Cleave feat (D20 Modern, p. 81). This stance does not end if you move at a lower Speed Rank, though it offers no benefit until you start moving at Speed Rank 1 or higher again.</p>\n\n\n\n",
